  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC435">
        <l>etirmaṟai yecca metirmaṟai muṭipiṉa.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/241/mode/1up">241</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/241/mode/1up">241</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, niṟutta muṟaiyāṉē etirmaṟaiyeccattiṟku muṭipu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : etirmaṟai yeccam eṉpaṉa iraṇṭu, ōkāra etirmaṟaiyum ummai yetirmaṟaiyum eṉa ; avai, avaitam etirmaṟaip poruḷkoṇṭu muṭiyum, eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'yāṉō koṇṭēṉ' eṉpatu; yāṉōvaṉṟē koṇṭēṉ eṉṟālum, ataṉāl apporuḷ koṇṭu muṭintatu eṉappaṭum. 'nīyē koṇṭāy' eṉṟāṟku etirmaṟuttavāṟu, 'yāṉ koṇṭileṉ' eṉa eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṉi, ummaiyetirmaṟai, 'varalum uriyaṉ' eṉpatu. āṇṭu, 'varalum' eṉappaṭṭa ummai yetirmaṟai, uriyaṉ eṉap piṉṉum avaṉaiyē koṇṭumuṭintatu. vārāmaiyum uriyaṉ eṉpataṟku etirmaṟai, avai oṉṟoṉṟaṉai nōkka etirmaṟai yeṉṟavāṟāyiṟṟu.	(39)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

